375 Morningstar Road, at the S.E. corner of Becks Lane. Beers's and Robinson's maps of 1874 and 1898, respectively, show the house to have belonged to H. Decker; the Robinson 1907 atlas and the Bromley 1917 atlas indicate it as the John D. Williams house.

May 4, 1932

P. L. Sperr
